        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Higher Education Access and Success for Homeless and Foster Youth Act</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Higher Education Act of 1965 to revise provisions related to financial aid and higher education programs for children and youths who are homeless or in foster care.</p>      <p>]]></text>
